\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3847ae06170a60a4c3be0d5b453c108e72aa3e62","tid":1800563,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05af08d436d5ae858264da8c9f5f8ff7880cf32","tid":1800563,"uid":54824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:30:07.000Z","msg":"簽咗請push<br />\n多啲人睇到"},{"pid":"bc2545a22c4982deecd3043be47ea10f0993e85f","tid":1800563,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c38676350cbf7062f198ddb5f4e3c117b6c7e99c","tid":1800563,"uid":20725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"啱啱簽左"},{"pid":"10b53177feeeb6c7c7c67936173376ddb7fadbfa","tid":1800563,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講差幾多人"},{"pid":"10b46e75615a7c040825d7acd9b0a880c3190f5c","tid":1800563,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>SHOP商場戰略檢討與重點</ins></strong></span> 幫手share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins><strong>1) 落閘就目標已達成, 可以轉場</strong></ins></span><br />\n商場落閘基本上都係因為D狗入撚哂黎, 咁達成目標 無需要再屌狗同戀戰<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>2) 街坊被捕個時麻煩街坊咪撚係度嘈</ins></strong></span><br />\n琴日已經有幾次係因為街坊太嘈, 個街坊大聲叫都無人聽到佢講乜, 咁樣同害9自己友無分別。一陣無名無姓無資料, 係咪想人地被消失??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>3) 回馬槍，D狗走個時唔撚好再上前</ins></strong></span><br />\n尤其是商場入面，次撚次比人回馬槍幾次。每次都捉撚左2-3個。屌狗還屌狗, 你地係後面屌就爽, 企前面既街坊就中伏。唔好再做豬隊友<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>4) 12點好撤，再留係度攬炒指數低</ins></strong></span><br />\n咁夜對政權既傷害係邊度? 個撚個都返鳩哂屋企訓教, 車又少。同玩平原戰 自殺有咩分別? 大家要記住個目標係乜野。街上又無其他路人幫你地cover, 過左12點又無車走。好似琴日MK咁, D人又話走唔撚到比狗包圍住。咪撚再要呀寶出動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">[告急] 德國人權法30號截,差22K, 用chrome簽, <br />\nchrome可以幫你翻譯做中文, <br />\n唔撚洗睇教學都識簽 洗撚睇教學咩<br />\n直接right click 轉做中文啦 好撚易之嘛</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_10%2F_01%2FPetition_99914.nc.html&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=bb9d2a5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_10/_01/Petition_99914.nc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJuUQZm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJuUQZm.png&h=76bbc9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OL5471p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOL5471p.png&h=1335725b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8b82a631241b56c62e439a3f9a8aa87b161c999","tid":1800563,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:33:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"acefa1d67e9bcfbba857b41121f94870f403856d","tid":1800563,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b53177feeeb6c7c7c67936173376ddb7fadbfa","tid":1800563,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T10:35:16.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講差幾多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"萬九<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671dc13b62afc95174eef81f208fac33fd42e74e","tid":1800563,"uid":184992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947773425c21deb7b53d8525933c064d024e99d8","tid":1800563,"uid":303988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"Done"},{"pid":"ab549659